    <p>Thai restau­rant Blue Jas­mine has ex­panded its se­lec­tion of plant-based dishes, many of which are ve­gan. They in­clude veg­e­tar­ian fried rice with Quorn nuggets bento ($15 nett), which also has a ve­gan op­tion; the ve­gan Heura red curry ($18 nett); and OMN! basil kaprao bento ($18 nett). To­mor­row, the restau­rant will of­fer all 10 of its bento boxes at $10 nett and 30 per cent off all dishes when you or­der via its e-store. Avail­able for de­liv­ery ($15). WHERE: Blue Jas­mine, Level 5 Park Ho­tel Far­rer Park, 10 Far­rer Park Sta­tion Road MRT: Far­rer Park</p>
    <p>WHEN: Lunch: 11am - 3pm daily; din­ner: 6.30 - 10pm daily; pro­mo­tion to­mor­row: 11am - 9pm</p>
    <p>TEL: 6824-8851</p>
    <p>INFO: www.face­book.com/ blue­jas­mine.sg</p>


